description: This beautiful, one of a kind, Craftsman-Style home can be yours! Three lots convey with home. Custom-built in 1992, tastefully refurbished since 2014. This 3 bedroom/2 bath/enclosed sun porch/2 car garage/2,000+ sq ft home has an above-ground pool with custom decking. The home is Frank Loyd Wright inspired, from the exterior design to the interior custom doors and light fixtures. Family room has wood burning fireplace. Formal dining are has open bay window. Eat-in-kitchen, smooth-top surface range, pantry. Kitchen appliances convey. You may access the pool from the enclosed porch area or the master suite. The asking price and this transaction includes the two open lots next to the home to the street which equals a little more than one full acre.
